description: Mixed use development comprising residential units (conventional two storey housing up to seven storey apartments at Blocks A, B, C, D (plots 124-256), Blocks E and F (plots 360-385) providing a range of 1-4 bed units): change of use to employment (Hotel): commercial use (B1, A1-A3): community facility: formal/incidental amenity space, landscaping and associated infrastructure and car parking.
